### Health Check
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:4000/

### Register User
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:4000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@dermatouch.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Get Profile (requires token)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Categories
GET http://localhost:4000/api/categories

### Get Products
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products

### Get Products with Search
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products?search=serum&page=1&limit=5

### Get Products by Category
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products?categoryId=1

### Get Single Product
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products/1

### Create Product (Admin only)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "New Product",
  "description": "Product description",
  "price": 1999.99,
  "sku": "NEW-PROD-001",
  "stock": 25,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### Create Order (requires token)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ],
  "address": {
    "street": "123 Main Street",
    "city": "Mumbai",
    "state": "Maharashtra",
    "zipCode": "400001",
    "country": "India"
  }
}

### Get User Orders
GET http://localhost:4000/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Orders (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/orders/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE